        <specpara>
            <important>
                <para>The rightmost switch of the tachometer DIP switches (# 10) is for selecting odometer mode - in
                    miles or kilometers. Position "1" is for kilometers. Position "0" is for miles.
                </para>
            </important>
        </specpara>
